title: Fart Kakl (aka Perdak Kakla)
description:
This game is about the situation in Ukraine.
Kakl - the main character of the game. He wants to go to the European Union, but can not.
He jumps and shit by shit, collects coins (Euros). When will collect a lot of coins, then buys a alco drink and now aspires to the EU is not alone.



- Over 50 000 installs

- Very famous game in Russia and Ukraine

- Many complaints and threats to developer

- 4.5 rating points

- Funny indie game

- Leader board, try be BEST gamer

- NO app purchases
